---
/**
 * Giscus comments — GitHub Discussions powered, no spam, AdSense-safe.
 *
 * Reader logs in with GitHub to comment. Discussion per article auto-created
 * on first comment using the article's pathname as the unique key.
 *
 * Config locked to:
 *   repo:        schul92/migukstory
 *   repo-id:     R_kgDOSgLQ3w
 *   category:    Announcements (maintainer-restricted to prevent random threads)
 *   category-id: DIC_kwDOSgLQ384C9RY6
 *   mapping:     pathname  (each /blog/[slug] gets its own discussion)
 *   lang:        ko
 *
 * Prereq: giscus GitHub app must be installed on the repo:
 *   https://github.com/apps/giscus → Install → select schul92/migukstory
 */
---

<section class="comments-section">
	<header class="comments-head">
		<h2>댓글</h2>
		<p class="comments-sub">
			GitHub 계정으로 댓글을 남길 수 있습니다 · 스팸 차단 · 공개 토론
		</p>
	</header>

	<script
		src="https://giscus.app/client.js"
		data-repo="schul92/migukstory"
		data-repo-id="R_kgDOSgLQ3w"
		data-category="Announcements"
		data-category-id="DIC_kwDOSgLQ384C9RY6"
		data-mapping="pathname"
		data-strict="1"
		data-reactions-enabled="1"
		data-emit-metadata="0"
		data-input-position="bottom"
		data-theme="light"
		data-lang="ko"
		data-loading="lazy"
		crossorigin="anonymous"
		async
	></script>
</section>

<style>
	.comments-section {
		max-width: var(--reading-width);
		margin: var(--s-5) auto var(--s-4);
		padding: var(--s-3) var(--s-2);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
	}
	.comments-head {
		margin-bottom: var(--s-3);
	}
	.comments-head h2 {
		font-family: var(--font-display);
		font-size: 1.6rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.3em;
		color: var(--ink);
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}
	.comments-sub {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--ink-light);
		margin: 0;
	}
	/* Style the giscus iframe wrapper */
	:global(.giscus) {
		margin-top: var(--s-2);
	}
</style>
